            <title>[GROOVY-6426] groovysh not running using the groovy-all jar</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-6426</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Basically the work done earlier for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-3079&quot; title=&quot;groovysh does not run when CLASSPATH includes embeddable/groovy-all.jar&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;GROOVY-3079&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;GROOVY-3079&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; didn&apos;t survive m18n refactoring. The jarjar task has some excludes for a class that has moved into a subproject.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
